  SNYK-DOTNET-MESSAGEPACK-17318029:
    - '*':
        reason: >-
          MessagePack is a transitive runtime dependency
          (Microsoft.VisualStudio.LanguageServer.Client > StreamJsonRpc) whose loaded version is
          provided by the Visual Studio host at runtime, not shipped/controlled by this extension.
          A direct PackageReference pins it to the fixed 2.5.301, but the manifest-level scan still
          reports StreamJsonRpc's declared 2.4.35. Same runtime-dependency category as the other
          ignores here -
          https://docs.snyk.io/scan-applications/supported-languages-and-frameworks/.net#tackling-vulnerabilities-from-runtime-dependencies
        expires: 2027-06-15T00:00:00.000Z
        created: 2026-06-15T00:00:00.000Z
